item.title: .JAR Problems need help
item.dc:creator: @beast14 beast14
item.description:
@beast14 wrote:

[quote=“1 2 3 4 KOED, post:2, topic:542106”]Right click the “run” in your client folder and click edit.
This is mine "java -Xmx512m com.Client 30 0 highmem members 32"
So I will set the manifest in my jar maker to “com.Client” It is also case sensitive too. Yours will probably be different as most of them are “client”. Hope this helped :)[/quote]

item.description:

Right click the “run” in your client folder and click edit.
This is mine "java -Xmx512m com.Client 30 0 highmem members 32"
So I will set the manifest in my jar maker to “com.Client” It is also case sensitive too. Yours will probably be different as most of them are “client”. Hope this helped
